  "prompt": "Which cold coffee is the best in CCD?",
  "response": "Caf\u00e9 Coffee Day (CCD) offers a variety of cold coffee options, and the \"best\" one depends on your personal taste preferences. Here are some popular cold coffee options at CCD that you might enjoy:\n\n1. **Iced Caffe Americano**  \n   - A refreshing and strong cold coffee made with espresso shots and chilled water. Perfect for those who enjoy a bold coffee flavor without milk.\n\n2. **Iced Caf\u00e9 Latte**  \n   - A creamy and smooth blend of espresso and cold milk, served over ice. It\u2019s a classic choice for those who enjoy a balanced coffee with a touch of sweetness.\n\n3. **Iced Caramel Coffee**  \n   - A sweet and indulgent option made with espresso, cold milk, and caramel syrup, served over ice. Ideal for those with a sweet tooth.\n\n4. **Cold Coffee with Ice Cream**  \n   - A rich and creamy treat made with coffee, milk, and a scoop of vanilla ice cream. It\u2019s a dessert-like option that\u2019s perfect for cooling off.\n\n5. **Iced Mocha**  \n   - A chocolatey cold coffee made with espresso, cold milk, and chocolate syrup. Great for those who love the combination of coffee and chocolate.\n\n6. **Iced Hazelnut Coffee**  \n   - A nutty and aromatic cold coffee made with hazelnut syrup, espresso, and cold milk. It\u2019s a flavorful option for hazelnut lovers.\n\nUltimately, the best cold coffee for you depends on whether you prefer a strong, creamy, sweet, or chocolatey flavor. If you\u2019re unsure, you can always ask the staff at CCD for recommendations based on your taste!",
